61 Ogre Warlord<br>
Solusek Ro</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=phantron>Phantron</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/03 12:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2853.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: My Suggestion on Hybrid Question</span><hr size=1> I'm not sure what your problem with defensive is.  It's absolutely godly on PoP mobs.  Sure it renders all our other discs obselete, but how many disc do you really see other melees use besides the equivalent of Fell Strike and the rare invulnerable disc?  Okay Monks use Stonestance on a regular basis, but that's about it.<br>
<br>
